{
  "chapter": 15,
  "chapter_summary": "第十五回大衍十式。辛捷以奇门五行之术帮助平凡上人走出困其十年的石笋阵，出阵后平凡上人心境豁然开朗。世外三仙之一慧大师赶到，与平凡上人对峙。辛捷接受慧大师三招考验，以虬枝剑法梅花三弄和平凡上人所授大衍十式方生不息化解攻势。平凡上人与慧大师展开千招大战，辛捷从中领悟大衍十式精微变化。鹤唳老人骑鹤而来，以啸声化解争斗，平凡上人随其而去。慧大师将诘摩神步传授辛捷，海潮冲毁脚印，辛捷凭天资领悟神步。辛捷乘船返回大陆，抵达武汉山梅珠宝店，惊闻侯二叔被人击毙。辛捷悲愤交加，在侯二叔墓前立誓追查凶手。随后在林中发现虬髯大汉与一名被点穴青年搏斗，辛捷出手相助，识出虬髯大汉为中州一剑孟非。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "从乾位进入，按左三右四之则，就能进人阵心，但出去时，却不大相同——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "从阵心向左转进，两次回绕后，应该有一人为的假笋——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "正是，正是！上次我从这条路绕去，正是有一人为的假石笋——看来你还真有一套，咱们这就走出去吧！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "只是晚辈对此古阵最多懂得十之六七，若是此阵布得完整，只怕仍是走不出去呢！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "不管它，咱们且试它一试。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "请前辈将此石笋毁去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来这慧大师对此阵功夫也没有学全，否则晚辈也无法走出了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "对了，你既是七妙神君的弟子，自然懂得那什么奇门五行的鬼门道了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "晚辈这点末行，实在难入行家法眼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "娃儿休要假谦虚伪，倒是我老儿方才施给你看的那“大衍十式”，你可曾仔细记住？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "晚辈正要感谢前辈以不世绝学相授——",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "只是晚辈一时有些地方还不能完全领会。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "老蠙对这几招剑法自认还有几分满意，那最后三招你须好好研究，若是发挥得宜，普天之下能接得下的，只怕寥寥无几呢！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "text": "老尼婆千方百计要占我老儿上风，可是老天有眼，偏偏总不如你意，哈哈！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "慧大师",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "老尼活到现在才第一次听说打赌要靠小辈助胜的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "text": "咱们当年打赌时可没有规定不准别人自动进来带我老儿出去吧？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "慧大师",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "看不出你这小娃儿居然认识我这古阵，须知你未经许可，擅人本岛，已是犯了重规，复又擅入石笋阵，更是罪不可恕，我倒要看看什么人胆敢不把老尼放在眼内。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "text": "晚辈擅人贵岛，本为无心之过，若是前辈定要以此为由教训晚辈，晚辈不才，却知头可折志不可屈！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "text": "老尼婆这小岛也有许多臭规矩，今日若不是这娃儿及时赶到，你这小岛此刻怕已在万丈海底了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "慧大师",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "你既能经得住我“咤阳玄音”想来必有几分功力，你有胆接老尼三招么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "text": "晚辈不自量力，就接前辈高招。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "慧大师",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "老咈啊，好一招“方生不息”！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "text": "是又怎样？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "慧大师",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "咱们有言在先，只对三招，你现在可以走了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "慧大师",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "老尼不识相，还要领教你老咈的‘大衍十式’。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "text": "就是老儿我也觉手痒得紧，咱们走几招杀杀闷正好。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "慧大师",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "询摩神步传与有缘，半个时辰内能不能领悟，就要看你的天资了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_ge",
      "text": "张大哥——",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_ge",
      "speaker_name": "张大哥",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "辛老板，你回来啦，小的望你回来都等到眼穿啦——",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_ge",
      "text": "什么？张大哥——",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_ge",
      "speaker_name": "张大哥",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "侯老他……他死去了——",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_ge",
      "text": "什么！你是说——你是说侯二叔已经去世……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_ge",
      "speaker_name": "张大哥",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "此话说来甚长，容小的进店再告——",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_ge",
      "text": "侯二叔到底怎么样啦！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_ge",
      "speaker_name": "张大哥",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "他死——",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "侯二叔是怎样死的？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_ji",
      "speaker_name": "伙计",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "十余天前，张大哥凌晨时在厢房天井中发现侯老躺在地上，已然死去，原先还以为是一时中风致死，但后来见他背上似乎受有内伤伤痕，这才知是受人击毙，张大哥急得要死，以为辛老板和武林人物交往而招致大祸，又怕匪徒再度来临，当时人心恇惴，曾一度准备解散店务，昨日才送了侯老的丧，好在今日老板回来了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_zhang_da_ge",
      "text": "侯二叔葬在什么地方呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_da_ge",
      "speaker_name": "张掌柜",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "小的平日素知辛老板甚敬重侯老，所以擅自主张动用厚金葬了侯老，墓地就在城外不远的西方一个山岗上。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_ran_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "蛧风大汉",
      "listener": "char_shou_chi_duan_zhi_de_ren",
      "text": "吕，看你再想逃——",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 407
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_meng_fei",
      "text": "兄台可是号称中州一剑的孟非？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_meng_fei",
      "text": "久闻大名，如雷灌耳——",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "孟非",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "罢了，罢了，自此——唉！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 448
    }
  ],
